    - @stack.lessons.each do |lesson|
      .stack-show-lesson
        = link_to lesson do
          .stack-index_body
            .stack-show-lesson_body_summary Lesson           
            .stack-show-lesson_body_title= lesson.title
            .stack-show-lesson_body_summary           
              The Beginning WordPress track trains one on how to be a WordPress Power Use.
